"P882332372" "Your hunch proved to be correct.  This is definitely the place, you hear the muffled cries of hostages in between orders barked by soldiers."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4079155156" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cracked Cell Phone</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You freed the foreign dignitary taken by the Arachnos Operative, prevented an international incident by saving the dignitaries and uncovered a plot to detonate a chemical weapon."

