"P1181197695" "You're sick and tired of 'saving the day' only to have the same criminals out on the street time and time again.  It's time to take the fight to those that threaten the people of your city.<br><br>You just intercepted a badly garbled police scanner message from a hero, stating that the Arachnos Operative in question's true goal was to detonate a chemical weapon in the area."
