// Clue Name :
"P1621910902" "Grim news..."
// DetailString :
"P3845849284" "Shade Edge lets you know that his two allies are in trouble.  Dusk Song was gravely injured during their battle and Psi Knight was rapidly beginning to change.  He sounded surprised that he was able to contact you from here considering his condition.  Finally, he begs you to keep his identity a secret."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DuskSongsays 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1257823858" "A dark reveal..."
// DetailString :
"P3511556582" "Dusk Song, says to you: 'It is too late for Psi Knight.  He has changed already and his mind is lost.  He must have called out to you just before being consumed by the mutagen.  Please, ease his suffering...'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1939977550" "There's no replacing a good hero, and you think you might be able to send help to deal with the situation in the sewers.  If you can get those heroes out of here fast enough, you might be able to deliver the antidote before they are too far gone."
// AcceptString :
"P2238922430" "Free the beleaguered heroes!"
// SendOffString :
"P2991000835" "While you've never met Psi Knight personally, you've heard many great things about him and what he has done for the city.  He has psychically broadcast the coordinates of his location to you. "
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1698066780" "Free Psi Knight and his allies."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2782149953" "Psi Knight's team deperately needs your help!  They're currently being held in a nearby cave network.  Help them, before it's too late."
// TaskTitle :
"P2044156667" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Voice In Your Head</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3957771206" "Agonizing groans and panicked voices are drowned out by the deep gutteral sounds being made by the Devouring Earth in these caves."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2636371076" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Voice In Your Head</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You freed Psi Knight's teammates and administered the antidote to both of them, but unfortunately it was too late for Psi Knight himself.  With deep regret, you ended his suffering.  His sacrifice shall not be made in vain."

