// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2857103331" "Jameson's regrets..."
// DetailString :
"P4293676886" "'If only I had been there {HeroName}.  I could have stopped the bombing....but, all my friends are dead because of her...  I understand what you're trying to do...just don't let her get away.  Please.'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PolarShiftClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3933633592" "Polar Shift's ramblings..."
// DetailString :
"P2654296295" "I admit it.  It was me, I destroyed their base.  Had I not done that, we'd have a mess on our hands.  Do you have any idea how far Nemesis' infiltration into our city goes?  DO YOU?  He's everywhere...everywhere...they're all automatons!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P426377515" "Longbow has overstepped their boundaries and is seeking revenge on their fallen allies by going after Polar Shift, whom they believe bombed one of their bases.  Polar Shift should be subject to a jury of her peers, not be victim to a bloodthirsty mob.<br><br>With that in mind this Longbow Officer must be stopped and Polar Shift must be brought to justice."
// AcceptString :
"P3571029586" "Stop Longbow Officer and arrest Polar Shift"
// SendOffString :
"P3168485514" "Nobody is above the law.  Not yourself, not Polar Shift and most certainly not Longbow.  It's time to remind all parties involved where their duties and allegiances should lie, with the people of Paragon City."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1556899123" "You must prevent Officer Jameson from making a critical mistake in judgment.  Stop Jameson and arrest Polar Shift."
// TaskTitle :
"P2816506320" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>'I don't care.  I want her dead!'</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1161710223" "You can hear Longbow agents barking orders as they search these halls for Polar Shift.  You've got to hurry before they go to far."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2161813654" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>'I don't care.  I want her dead!'</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to stop the Longbow Officer, and his men from killing Polar Shift as well as arresting Polar Shift so she can stand trial for what she is accused of doing.  Before she was handed off to the authorities, she rambled on about a Nemesis plot and his automatons replacing everyone."

