// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RescuedPolarShift 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1741154811" "Polar Shift rambles.."
// DetailString :
"P1532977635" "You.  You're not one of them, no you can't be.  You fought them.  Unless this is some sort of trick.   No...no you're real.  I'll let you in on a little secret.  They're automatons!  Fakes!  Machines!  Well, at least some of them are.  Nemesis has infiltrated Longbow and replaced many of their agents with automatons!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SuspiciousCrate 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3869127205" "Automaton Parts"
// DetailString :
"P3799312762" "You find a crate with a bunch of mismatched parts, that appear to be Nemesis automatons modeled after Longbow agents.  The uncanny resemblance to human beings chills you to the bone and the realization of what this means is horrifying."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2076732882" "Longbow is hunting down this Hero of the city.  She's done great things for Paragon City and you're not about to let them get their filthy hands on her.  Polar Shift operates on a level similar to your own.  Sometimes you've got to work on the outside of the law to do what's right.<br><br>You plan on saving Polar Shift before she's nabbed by Longbow."
// AcceptString :
"P3593743167" "Free Polar Shift from Longbow"
// SendOffString :
"P729497163" "Like Polar Shift, you are often forced to make tough decisions for the greater good.  You can relate to her and know what it's like to feel vilified for doing what you know to be right.  It's time to get your sister in arms out of there and away from Longbow's clutches."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P647700852" "If Polar shift is killed, Paragon City will suffer.  The city needs more heroes like her, ones who are willing to make difficult choices others don't have the guts to make.  You have to stop this Officer Jensen, before it's too late!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3133034532" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>'I don't care.  I want her dead!'</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P687693514" "You can hear Longbow agents barking orders as they search these halls for Polar Shift.  You've got to hurry before they go too far."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1423400218" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>'I don't care.  I want her dead!'</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to rescue Polar Shift, she rambled on about a Nemesis plot and his automatons replacing everyone.  Evidently she bombed the Longbow base, because she discovered hard evidence that some of their agents had been replaced by Nemesis automatons.  That's a frightening revelation."

