// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - NemesisBossClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3635474148" "A Nemesis Plot?"
// DetailString :
"P807374812" "You defeated the conspirator behind the bomb threat and his automaton army.  Before you took him into custody he told you that 'Lord' Nemesis has been keeping tabs on you."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3336727181" "Somewhere nearby a building is rigged with explosives and is set to detonate in the very near future unless the Nemesis officer's demands are met.  Despite this possibly being a trap, you can't rest while there is even a chance of innocent citizens being in harm's way."
// AcceptString :
"P1548972474" "Diffuse Nemesis bomb threat!"
// SendOffString :
"P3709014719" "Sometimes you have to chance it, you can't risk the lives of the civilians inside this office building.  Trap or no, you've got to see this through.  Disarming the bombs is the only certain way to make sure the people are safe."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2550075755" "According to the Nemesis Officer's threat, a nearby office building is rigged to blow.  You've got to get in there and disarm those bombs and save the office workers before anyone is hurt."
// TaskTitle :
"P3599503381" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Obvious Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3877043585" "You hear office workers going about their business.  Everyone seems oblivious to the bomb threat.  Something isn't right here..."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P752925287" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Obvious Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>This was clearly a trap set up specifically for the heroes of Paragon City, and you fell for it hook, line and sinker.  But, it seems almost too obvious...  What is Nemesis playing at?  Is he testing you?"

