"P3520672262" "The survivor's story"
// DetailString :
"P2201873761" "This woman explains to you she has been injected with some sort of strange serum that has infected her with some sort of fever that never goes away.  The guards nearly gunned her down, when her binds melted right off her body."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - CaptiveClue2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2270991855" "Poor man..."
// DetailString :
"P2525512057" "You have a hard time understanding this fellow you managed to save.  Physically he seems to be in tiptop shape, however mentally...he appears to have completely lost his mind.  Hopefully with the right treatment he can live a normal life once again."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ComputerClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1977764872" "Crey Experiment Data"
// DetailString :
"P4189618969" "You download data regarding the experiments performed on the captives here.  Your pulse races and your blood runs cold when you think of what happened to the people here.  Crey must be brought to justice for their crimes!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2864869809" "You help the battered man up, who has gone through more than you can imagine, and make sure he is brought to a hospital.  Before he is taken away by paramedics he gives you the location of the Crey laboratory where the others were kept."
// AcceptString :
"P4082660248" "Rescue the citizens before it's too late."
// SendOffString :
"P1250427365" "Those citizens have likely gone through terrible experiments and it may be too late for them.  However, you can't take that chance.  As a hero of Paragon City, it is your duty to try and save them."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3674851263" "Free the Crey captives!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3921787248" "Crey has been experimenting on the citizens of the city.  You can't let this stand.  For now, you need to save those victims before it's too late."
// TaskTitle :
"P2123717077" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P281337417" "Over the dull hum of the lighting you hear the distinct sound of a man screaming in agony in the distance."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1562868865" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to free three captives taken by Crey for unspeakable experiments.  It sickens you to know how untouchable Crey is despite all the evidence stacked against them."

