"P3308907896" "They'll never knew what him them."
// DetailString :
"P1255549128" "An explosive like this is capable of shredding an industrial compound such as this with ease, you brought three just for good measure."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3810079155" "It's most likely too late for those citizens.  They're likely either already dead or so far gone to save anymore anyhow.  It's time to bring the fight to Crey.  You have several plastic explosive charges with their name on it.  This will show Crey what happens to those who hurt the people of your city."
// AcceptString :
"P1392010325" "Destroy the Crey Lab"
// SendOffString :
"P1802409805" "You'll show Crey what happens to those who cross the line.  This will be a message they will understand loud and clear and not forget anytime soon.  You help the injured man up and set out on your way."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2288519099" "Bomb the Crey Lab"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P43895125" "You're sick and tired of Crey getting away with murder, often literally.  It's time to stop this.  You need to bomb their laboratory to end this.  Maybe then they'll back off."
// TaskTitle :
"P3500975239" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1173311639" "Soon, this Crey laboratory will be a smoking crater."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1543054997" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You press the detonator and watch as the entire building is engulfed in flame in a blink of an eye.  You doubt there will be any survivors, but that's the price for working with Crey."

