"P3072501975" "Jackpot!"
// DetailString :
"P652112962" "This computer has files outlining all of the activities performed by 5th Column bases in the area and where they are located.  You can do some serious damage with this information."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2486525330" "That traitor knew what he was getting himself into when he enlisted.  The only way to take down an organization is go after its many heads and cut them off, one by one.  Eliminating every 5th Column soldier in that base is the best way to gather information on other 5th Column bases.  You might even uncover the identity of their shadowy leader."
// AcceptString :
"P3966126773" "Uncover information at key 5th Column base."
// SendOffString :
"P2917426025" "You flip through the filthy pages of the journal and stumble upon some vital information describing a central headquarters in the vicinity.  This base coordinates the efforts of the 5th Column in the entire region according to the journal."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2747903266" "Get information from 5th Column Base"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2492379125" "The 5th Column is a blight upon this city and you have the opportunity of a lifetime to get some information to hit them where it will truly hurt.  It's time to set off and deal with this threat."
// TaskTitle :
"P164099745" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Blood Spattered Journal</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4120510924" "This has got to be the place.  You hear 5th Column propaganda being broadcast throughout the caves."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1717648434" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Blood Spattered Journal</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Given enough time, resources and man power you will be able to bring the 5th Column to its knees with the data you've collected today.  These files outline the greater 5th Column agenda in this region, and you'll be able to foil them at each step."

