// Clue - KeyClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P35011351" "'They changed them!'"
// DetailString :
"P3536648314" "It's terrible, I know we must resist the insane things they've tried to convince us of.  I managed to hang on for as long as I could.  Some of the others weren't so fortunate, they were carted off to a lab and...changed...before being brought back here.  Maybe you can save them {HeroName}!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BrainwashedConscriptClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P504900573" "Brainwashed Conscript"
// DetailString :
"P540106342" "This Brainwashed Conscript was once a man, he has gone through a horrible transformation.  Perhaps with the right help he can return to being a human being once again."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P315599561" "This data indicates that around half a dozen young men were kidnapped from different parts of Paragon City to be brainwashed at the Council Indoctrination Center hidden somewhere in the vicinity.  Those young men need your help before they are corrupted by the Council."
// AcceptString :
"P432471707" "Free the Council Conscripts"
// SendOffString :
"P1083410500" "These young men were taken against their will and have their whole lives ahead of them.  You can't allow these conscripts to be brainwashed and experimented on.  You take note of the indoctrination's secret location and head off."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3775950101" "You've got to stop this.  If the Council brainwashes innocent people it means that they'll not only swell their ranks, but completely ruin a life in the process."
// TaskTitle :
"P375973570" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Curious Black Jewel Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2535347747" "You've got a pretty good hunch that this is the place.  Next to the door are bound piles of Council propaganda that you normally see posted all around shadier parts of the city."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2525721682" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Curious Black Jewel Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to save 4 of the young men, sadly two were subjected to the Council's experiments and turned into the horrible creatures that make up the Council's legions.  You brought them in with the hopes that perhaps someday they could be returned to normal."

