// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ExperimentsClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4001760789" "Council Experiments"
// DetailString :
"P2091405853" "The files on this computer outlines the most recent experimentations made on normal human beings.  Evidently they've been trying to convert regular humans to Vampyri with incredibly low success rate.  Out of the dozens captured only three managed to survive the process."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SelfDestructClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P270081193" "Self Destruct Activated"
// DetailString :
"P3791305398" "After entering the head researcher's codes you activate the base's self destruct sequence.  In a few short minutes this laboratory will be no more."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - VampyriChamberClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2495555139" "Vampyri Chambers"
// DetailString :
"P3555882809" "These are modified versions of the Vampyri Chambers used in Striga Isle that are capable of transforming even normal human beings, although with a very low success rate.  From the sound of it, more people have been harmed or killed than turned into Vampyri."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2750478405" "It's likely too late for those citizens, however it's not too late to prevent the Council from being able to continue with these horrible experiments.  Somewhere nearby is a laboratory being used for who knows what horrible purpose."
// AcceptString :
"P3873704170" "Destroy the Council Laboratory!"
// SendOffString :
"P1515066081" "You take note of the coordinates of this Council laboratory.  The Council is a plague on your city, and you must eradicate it wherever it is found.  This laboratory allows the council to make their Vampyri super soldiers and who knows whatever else.  It must be destroyed."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P288869105" "Destroy the Council Laboratory"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3563244913" "These experiments are inhuman, you can't allow this to continue.  You set off towards the location of the laboratory ready to handle this threat once and for all."
// TaskTitle :
"P1464185077" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Curious Black Jewel Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P813095979" "This place gives you the creeps.  Somewhere off in the distance you think you hear the muffled inhuman screams."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1991837477" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Curious Black Jewel Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Just for good measure, you set the base's self destruct system right before leaving.  In true heroic fashion flames spew from the cave entry just as you leap out unharmed, and with that the Council's plans to transform the citizens of Paragon City into Vampyri have been ended."

