// Clue Name :
"P194293820" "Secret Service Automaton"
// DetailString :
"P2915392008" "After sifting through this crate's contents you find a false bottom.  Once opened you discover parts to a Nemesis automaton that looks frighteningly like a Secret Service Agent."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AutomatonCrateClue2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3471962541" "Longbow Automaton"
// DetailString :
"P5771500" "Under the crate's false bottom you discover enough automaton parts to build a Longbow Agent.  For a brief moment you feel as if you're holding parts of a dismembered human, due to the realistic details captured by the automaton."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AutomatonCrateClue3 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P517270511" "It's....you?"
// DetailString :
"P904051614" "After tearing open this crate's false bottom you discover enough components to build an automaton copy of...you.  The attention to details are uncanny, only those who know your mannerisms would know the difference, and maybe not even then."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1092555614" "Arachnos or some other terrorist organization infiltrating a group like Longbow would be devastating.  You need to gather evidence before making any accusations or taking any action against Longbow, so you decide to investigate the source of the transmission."
// AcceptString :
"P2889999041" "Investigate the source of the transmission."
// SendOffString :
"P1968265478" "Before making a mess of things with Longbow, it's best to get evidence first.  It's too early to jump to conclusions and assume they've gone rogue.  You take note of the location of the signal's origin and head off to find out what is really going on."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3240309772" "Investigate the warehouse"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2712850290" "You hope to get to the bottom of these mysterious encryped broadcasts.  Investigating the source of them might be the best way to do this."
// TaskTitle :
"P1818337726" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Noise Within Noise</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3912636066" "You've arrived at the location of the mysterious transmission you overheard.  For a moment you hear nothing but the creaks and groans of an old building, but then you think you hear muffled voices in the distance."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2489511823" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Noise Within Noise</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You have uncovered a plot that must be brought to the attention of the entire city.  Nemesis could have placed automaton look alikes all over Paragon City.  How will we know fakes from the real thing?  Anyone could be a Nemesis automaton."

