// Clue - LongbowAutomatonClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// DetailString :
"P1709792087" "As soon as you open this crate and see its contents you know something is horribly wrong.  This crate is filled to the brim with enough parts to make half a dozen Nemesis Automatons fashioned after Longbow Agents.  This base has been compromised, it's best that you activate the base's self destruct system to purge the Nemesis threat, just to be sure.  You need to get out!  In the distance you hear the heavy bootfalls of Longbow Agents coming for you."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SelfDestructClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1468834301" "Self Destruct Sequence"
// DetailString :
"P1553219989" "Over the intercom you hear a pleasant and serene voice announce the impending destruction of this Longbow base."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2415398349" "Discovering if and where corruption lies is more of your line of work.  You think you can work your way into a Longbow base.  They shouldn't give you any trouble, and if they do that only proves they're guilty of conspiracy.  You think you'll investigate their base and see what you can find."
// AcceptString :
"P4191287860" "Investigate the Longbow base."
// SendOffString :
"P2966772205" "Everyone is corruptible, especially mercenaries like Longbow.  You've seen this sort of thing happen time and time again.  You've got a hunch that something isn't right here at all."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2673101018" "Investigate Longbow base"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P961679161" "You've got a nagging feeling that something is horribly wrong.  You really should get to that Longbow base to investigate."
// TaskTitle :
"P3081074508" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Noise Within Noise</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3415517887" "At first glance, this place appears like any other Longbow base.  It's best to give it a closer look though."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1315973752" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Noise Within Noise</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Initially everything appeared normal in the Longbow base, but as soon as you discovered a crate with Nemesis automaton parts in it fashioned after Longbow Agents the 'Agents' in the base immediately turned on you revealing themselves to be automatons themselves.  The only way to make sure this particular threat was contained was by destroying that Longbow base."

