// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1763681848" "Longbow has crossed the line, they should have known this is something you're not capable of doing!  How dare they doubt you.  Just as you're about to head off to the Longbow base an alert announces over your police band radio:<br><br><color orange>ALERT UPDATE<br><br>{HeroName} has been apprehended in a Longbow training facility!  PPD in route to detain and send to the Zig.</color><br><br>What in the world is going on?  Somehow this duplicate has managed to have gotten caught?"
// SendOffString :
"P802152524" "This is very strange.  Now there's more than one person, or <i>things</i> out there pretending to be you.  This ends now!  You figure you can kill two birds with one stone.  You can find out who's behind all of this and clear up the situation with Longbow simultaneously."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3708809976" "You're not sure how it's possible, but there's evidently more than one duplicate of you running around.  It's up you to stop them and clear your name."
// TaskTitle :
"P3395903134" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted Poster With Your Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2711524110" "As soon as you enter the Longbow base you notice security cameras pan on your position.  A moment later an alarm sounds."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3795521824" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Wanted Poster With Your Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You went into the Longbow base with the intent of confronting them about these charges, but instead were attacked by Longbow as they assumed you had escaped capture.  But, in reality, they had a mechanical copy of you detained, which you handily defeated.  This 'doppelganger' had similar powers to your own and looked identical to you, however you managed to clear your name after being able to explain the situation to the authorities."

