// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3149424470" "While you find it hard to believe violent, destructive, party animal hooligans like the Freakshow could actually turn their lives around and make something of themselves.  However, part of you hopes this is true.  It might be inspiring to other villains in Paragon City to see what these ex-criminals could do for society.  You don't condone stealing from the rich, or from anyone for that matter, but at least they're not killing innocent people.<br><br>This Freakshow educator and his pupils sound like they could use your help before the teacher's ex-gang members come and cause them harm."
// AcceptString :
"P736159299" "Help out Freakshow educator"
// SendOffString :
"P1525720470" "You take note of the warehouse where this violence is taking place and head off.  You hope you're not too late, these ex-Freakshow deserve a chance to straighten themselves out and this educator might be just the person to do it.  The Freakshow can likely relate to one of their own."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2016490586" "If these ex-Freakshow want to become functioning members of society, who are you to stand in their way.  You should give them a hand and prevent their ex-allies from stopping them."
// TaskTitle :
"P4083355752" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Truly Bizarre Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4009086681" "Total chaos has broken out in this warehouse.  You hear loud electronic music blasting in the distance which is drowning out the sound of violence."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4142791945" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Truly Bizarre Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>This ex-Freakshow who goes by the handle of "The Learner" has been teaching other Freakshow members interested in leading a 'normal' life.  While you were giving him direction on how to do this without committing crimes after bringing all of the violent Freakshow to justice, you were ambushed by Shock Treatment, a notorious Rogue Isles villain who was hellbent on destroying this schoolhouse for some reason.  She seemed to have an intense desire to crush the hopes and dreams of the ex-Freakshow."

