// RandomFameString :
"P286897873" "{HeroName}, I saw the freakiest thing yesterday.  This freakshow guy signed up for a business ethics course at my school.  He had a tie and everything.  How weird!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_11 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - StudentClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2664461717" "Pleas that fell on deaf ears.."
// DetailString :
"P2062192988" "This Freakshow begged you for mercy, however they'll not find any within you.  Did this ex-con give his many victims mercy?  No!  So, why should you?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ShockTreatmentClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3925341485" "Parlay!  Parlay!"
// DetailString :
"P2825963688" "After freeing Shock Treatment, a notoriously unstable Rogue Isles' villain she convinced you to let her join you.  Normally you wouldn't work with scum like this, but a little help will likely come in handy."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P281488503" "While you find it hard to believe violent, destructive, party animal hooligans like the Freakshow could actually turn their lives around and make something of themselves.  Whatever these freaks are up to will fail ultimately, they're animals and animals cannot deny their nature.  All they know is mindless violence, it's best to end this here and now.  The best way to go about doing that is to beat down those responsible for the violence: the leaders on both sides.  The educator Freakshow, his students and those leading the raid on the warehouse."
// AcceptString :
"P2082443982" "Defeat Freakshow Leaders"
// SendOffString :
"P2020510033" "These animals only understand one thing.  Violence.  That's the only way they learn.  No amount of books, education or self-help tapes will straighten these beasts out.  You take note of the warehouse where the Freakshow violence is happening and head off."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2750619393" "The Freakshow will always be mindless animals, it's time they learned their place.  You set off to deal with their ringleader."
// TaskTitle :
"P3783497457" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Truly Bizarre Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3926033482" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Truly Bizarre Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Freakshow in the warehouse turned schoolhouse were defiant.  Their leader "The Learner" swore he would rise up again and build his school again.  If that happens you will destroy it again, but next time it'll be with plastic explosives."

