// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_12 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Dirge 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3079576162" "The Dirge of Entropy"
// DetailString :
"P2372288047" "As the shadow cyst crystal is destroyed, several images flash before you, while the words 'Dirge of Entropy' echo in the area. The first image is of an Italian man being dragged away into the darkness. The second is of a fight on a train car. The last is an image from inside of an ancient cavern, possibly originating in the Roman times from the architecture. The images die down, with a dark voice speaking from somewhere...<br><br>'His power must be contained, unless he destroys us all.'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3980876575" "Letting the Council get away with this summoning is the only way to lure out whoever is truly behind this - what would be the point of stopping it now to only have it happen again? Sure, some people <i>will</i> be hurt if the Nictus are allowed to roam free, but it's the price that Paragon will have to pay to stay safe.<br><br>You'll bide your time and wait for the Council to make their move - that's when you'll spring into action."
// AcceptString :
"P3157917736" "Bide your time to lure out the Council leader!"
// SendOffString :
"P17600009" "You wait for some time until you hear news of the Nictus pouring out of a warehouse - this must have been where the Council were setting up, though knowing them, the true lair was in a cavern beneath it. <br><br>Rumor has it that a member of the Council was seen going into the warehouse - the exact man you're looking for! Time to go in there and strike at the heart of the Council's schemes!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P126684566" "Defeat the Council Agent!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1518846070" "With the other heroes in Paragon dealing with the Nictus, it'll be up to you to stop this."
// TaskTitle :
"P3604901110" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cloud of Odorous Smoke</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P209468729" "The walls of this warehouse pulse with the energy of the Nictus. And somewhere within here is the man who planned it all."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2767603990" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cloud of Odorous Smoke</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to stop the mastermind behind the organization of the Nictus, though it seems as if the Council was not aware of this man's actions. Regardless, with him put down, it should mean an end to this branch of the Nictus 'invasion'."

