// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_13 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Carnival 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3698137955" "Flambeaux's Mind Domination"
// DetailString :
"P1455312809" "The Carnival Mistress revealed to you that the once big-name heroine, Flambeaux, has been known to run with the Carnival of Shadows, using them to take down groups of Arachnos. Sometimes they mind control her, though the mistress notes that Flambeaux seems to actually <i>enjoy</i> some of the wanton destruction she wages while controlled, to the point where at moments she isn't even being controlled.<br><br>However, they do not fully trust Flambeaux, as she has on more than one occasion made a large spectacle out of burning down one of the Carnival's parties, letting the authorities in Paragon know that it was her doing by marking the ashes with the word 'Flammie'."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Arachnos 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P399203470" "Clone Technology"
// DetailString :
"P1151631373" "You demanded answers from the Crab Spider regarding clone technology that Arachnos has, given the statements made by the Rikti. The Arachnos agent refused to answer, despite your 'techniques' to make him talk. The only thing you got out of him was that Arachnos is working somewhere on technology to clone their operatives - something which the Rikti have taken great interest in."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Crey 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2696045571" "Crey's Movements"
// DetailString :
"P3517968549" "The Crey Researcher told you many, many interesting things regarding Crey Corp, though most of it was only from the stance of a low-level researcher. Two interesting notes were Crey's plans to steal Arachnos technology, specifically regarding their Bane Spiders, and a plan to develop a chemical that would detonate water. However, you were only able to find out that these 'may or may not be happening' - in other words, nothing concrete."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1789704772" "Doc Quantum has a good way of doing things. So what if one Longbow agent has been tossed to Arachnos? The information you'll get out of these three villains is well worth the price of some agent, who would have given her life to fight against Arachnos anyway.<br><br>It doesn't matter if she didn't exactly <i>know</i> she was going to do it this time - does Longbow ever fully disclose that information anyway?<br><br>Regardless, Quantum has set the gift up for you - it's time to collect, though you're slightly wary about <i>how</i> Quantum managed to gather all of these villains together in one place. You'll have to be on your guard."
// AcceptString :
"P1669420022" "Take down the three villains!"
// SendOffString :
"P3163879802" "You head to the office building that Doc Quantum specified. If this is a trap though, you'll be sure to pay the good doctor back."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3622452118" "Take down Quantum's villains!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1489589429" "Longbow will probably take care of that agent - they look after their own, after all."
// TaskTitle :
"P3277515544" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Beethoven's 5th Symphony</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2137381297" "You can already tell from the windows outside of this office building how Quantum got the villains here - the Rikti!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3873206560" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Beethoven's 5th Symphony</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step out from the office building to be greeted by Doc Quantum's hologram.<br><br>'{HeroName}, you performed admirably. You're someone who is willing to take risks to get what is needed done. People like us will move Paragon - and the world- forward. Please, I implore you, do keep in touch.'<br><br>As long as Quantum continues bringing in more results like this, you will."

