// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL6-7_Task_14 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Stalwart 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3760365942" "Stalwart's Regret"
// DetailString :
"P694094372" "You defeated the former boxer, Stalwart, who shared his regrets with you afterwards...<br><br><color LightGrey>Do you know what it's like, {HeroName}? To focus all of your life on one thing only to find out that you're just 'not good enough' anymore? I couldn't even save those pitiable Scrapyarders from the Cage Consortium...I couldn't save any of them! If I was just stronger...maybe I could have. <br><br>But I can't...I've reached my peak. I can't...I thought if I just had some more dyne...some more of the steroids...that I could push myself harder. It wasn't for me {HeroName}, it was so that I could protect the others.<br><br>Take me in, but I warn you. Those bars won't stop me from getting back out. Nothing will stop me from doing what's right - not even my own health."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1837943395" "All of the Family's main buyers will be gathered at this convention - this would be the perfect time to round them all up and bring them in. However you're aware that this place will be heavily guarded - both by the Family and whoever else might be there to purchase their goods. Not that it matters, really - since you'll make sure everyone there is taken down."
// AcceptString :
"P1900486751" "Take down the Family Drug Convention!"
// SendOffString :
"P1466775902" "You head off towards the location of the drug convention. You're going to show the Family that their drugs aren't welcome in this city - along with all of the people who do business with them."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P743942560" "Break up the Drug Convention!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P514063121" "You'll have to make sure to bring enough evidence so no one gets off on any loopholes."
// TaskTitle :
"P2690985273" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Denmark Wants Muscles This Friday</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3736331196" "There were several cars parked outside of the warehouse - however, they all seemed to belong to...Crey? Is Crey Industries trying to get in on the Family's turf?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1754430280" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Denmark Wants Muscles This Friday</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Paragon Police should be arriving to deal with everyone you took care of in that warehouse. It seems Antonino Marcone's influence within Crey was very widespread - enough to get other members of Crey to approve of the drug deal. You'll have to keep an eye out for this in the future."

