// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL6-7_Task_14 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P953255583" "<color orange>The Crey Security guard is speaking on a cellphone - his eyes widen as you come into view, reaching for a button to alarm the base to your presence."
// Answer Text :
"P670465051" "(Disarm the guard and question him)"
// Answer Text :
"P1375466514" "Push that button and it'll be the last thing you ever do."
// Answer Text :
"P3519754445" "(Leap forward and knock out the guard)"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2482351124" "<color orange>You disarm the guard and throw him to the ground. He lets out a groan of pain.</color><br><br>Ugh! L-let me go! What do you want with me?!"
// Answer Text :
"P434142627" "Tell me everything about what's going on here - now!"
// Page RuninFear Text :
"P3761142913" "O-okay! Antonino Marcone, he's with Crey! He convinced all of us we'd get paid big time if we helped out the Family with their drug trade! <br><br>Look, the other members of Crey don't know about this, I swear! And I'm not even a g-guard! I'm just an intern here! You gotta let me go! <color orange><br><br>With that information gleaned, you knock out the man, kicking him to the side.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1928517928" "The Family through Crey. That's enough for me to move forward."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P297480086" "<color orange>The guard freezes in place, staring at you in fear. His hand shakes before he drops the trigger for the alarm.</color><br><br>W-what do you want from me? Just tell me whatever it is! I don't want to get hurt!"
// Answer Text :
"P2879234390" "What is Crey doing in the drug trade?!"
// Page Guardtakedown Text :
"P3010616834" "<color Orange>The guard let's out a scream, which you quickly</color> <color red>silence</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3800908276" "Hmph. Now for the vault."
// Page GoodReason Text :
"P2626558719" "It was all Antonino Marcone's idea! He...he joined up with Crey, I don't know HOW he got in! But he's in! And he said if we worked with him we'd see our paychecks get real big! Listen, I'm just doing this for the money, I'm really not trying to hurt anyone, I swear! You gotta believe me!"
// Answer Text :
"P3579842437" "Why should I believe you're any better than the people here?"
// Page RunAlong Text :
"P1101966801" "<color orange>The guard runs up to you, pleading.</color><br><br>I'm just an intern! They told me if I helped out the Marcones with their drug trade that I'd make a lot of money! I didn't want to hurt anyone, I just wanted to get some more money, that's all, I swear!""
// Answer Text :
"P1331630811" "You disgust me! (Knock out the man)"
// Page BeneathMe Text :
"P1519360376" "<color Orange>The guard collapses at your feet."
// Answer Text :
"P1360436040" "That's that. Time to investigate this place..."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1978327979" "<color orange>You knock out the security guard, though you were unable to use him for any information regarding what's further on in this warehouse.."
// Answer Text :
"P2270975048" "Might as well keep moving forward."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3808152264" "Who exactly gets away at this drug convention doesn't matter to you - they can sell all the drugs they want, but they'll be in for a surprise when they find out that their main dealer has been hit - and hard. You're going to stalk out the warehouse location, wait for any of the higher ups in the Family to leave, then follow them to wherever they're keeping their money."
// AcceptString :
"P3772206839" "Destroy the Family's main source of income!"
// SendOffString :
"P1643845596" "You wait outside of the warehouse until you see something that catches you off guard - a higher up within Crey Corporation leaving the warehouse with several escorts, all of them putting large briefcases full of money into the back of a truck. <br><br>Something isn't right here...you begin to track the truck down, following it to a nearby Crey warehouse."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3233671044" "Investigate the...Crey Warehouse?"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1648022035" "What is Crey doing in the Family business?"
// TaskTitle :
"P1940529875" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Denmark Wants Muscles This Friday</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2894731194" "The warehouse is quiet - the man who brought in the money dropped it off somewhere deep inside of here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1403461194" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Denmark Wants Muscles This Friday</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You destroyed all the money that Crey and the Marcones made from the transactions, along with Antonino Marcone's allies within Crey. He'll be left without any resources now to peddle his wares - and he'll know that it was your doing. You can just imagine the fearful look on his face now."

