// Task - AM_Hero_SL6-7_Task_15 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Smith 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4207508948" "McHackerSmith's Words"
// DetailString :
"P422651125" "You rescued the man known as 'McHackerSmith', who had this to say to you...<br><br><color LightGrey>Thanks {HeroName}. My real name is William H. McSmith. You can kind of see where I got the name from. I've been a hacker on and off during the years before coming to work at this company. As much as I'd like to say I hacked the automatons on my own, I had help.<br><br>You might not believe it, but it was an AI program that helped me. Called itself AI Executable Number 6. It said it was created by Crey, but that it was now free on the internet. Me and it talk a lot, it's taking up some sorta crusade against Nemesis, Malta, and Crey. Looks like I'm at the forefront of it now too, huh?<br><br>Anyway, I'm the only human left here, but Sandy, the automaton I hacked, is still out here somewhere!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2157030973" "You can't just sit by why this civilian sits in this office building, waiting for the moment to come when the automatons will end his life. Even if it means losing out on the lead for this Nemesis warehouse, it's something you're willing to sacrifice. In the end, it's a smaller sacrifice than this man is willing to make, after all."
// AcceptString :
"P3228418881" "Save McHackerSmith and his co-workers!"
// SendOffString :
"P609627105" "You hurry towards the office where McHackerSmith is located, wary of who may or may not be an actual Nemesis automaton."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3758279389" "Save McHackerSmith!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3798388773" "Hopefully this post won't start a flamewar on the Nemesis Meme forums."
// TaskTitle :
"P2564665125" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Nemesis Meme</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3782205126" "The scorch marks littered across the walls means there was a fight here recently - did someone else show up to save the day?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3608557529" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Nemesis Meme</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>That's one office cleansed of the automatons. Bill McSmith will live another day, and with the help of AI Executable Number 6, continue the fight against Nemesis."

