// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PolarShift 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1629325430" "Polar Shift's Woe"
// DetailString :
"P1252790300" "Polar Shift nearly collapsed at your feet when you rescued her. Her eyes were red and worn, as if she hadn't slept for weeks.<br><br><color CadetBlue>Who is real {HeroName}? Are you real? Because they attacked you and me? Does that make you real? Are any of us real? Am...-I- real?!<br><br></color>Despite that, Polar Shift seems balanced enough for now to fight by your side."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Stalwart 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P973251289" "Automaton Stalwart"
// DetailString :
"P3250640091" "You defeated an automaton version of Stalwart within the factory. When it collapsed, you saw some imprints on the back of his head. It reads...<br><br><color CadetBlue>STALWART<br><br>NUMBER 4<br><br>WHA"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Flambeaux 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P756970938" "Automaton Flambeaux"
// DetailString :
"P3734917537" "You defeated an automaton of the vigilante Flambeaux. When it fell to the ground, you found some curious writing on her forehead - an oddly obvious place for it...<br><br><color CadetBlue>FLAMBEAUX<br><br>NUMBER 3<br><br>TIS"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Thystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1636853292" "Automaton Miss Thystle"
// DetailString :
"P1884221372" "You defeated an automaton of Miss Thystle, who is rumored to be trying to redeem herself. You found the following writing on her shoulder...<br><br><color CadetBlue>MISS THYSTLE<br><br>NUMBER 2<br><br>REAL?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P865130459" "McHackerSmith is a man who knows what the value of a person's life is worth. He's bought you the time needed to go to this warehouse and blow it up, halting a major production plant that Nemesis has of these automatons. They'll probably be busy trying to pack everything and move out - which means you'll have to strike this place, and fast!"
// AcceptString :
"P1047255579" "Destroy the Automaton Factory!"
// SendOffString :
"P4226045973" "You head off to blow up the warehouse at the expense of McHackerSmith's life. Hopefully those ungrateful people on the forums will learn from his example."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2076524756" "You'll have to be prepared for any mind tricks that Nemesis might play on you."
// TaskTitle :
"P1295529395" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Nemesis Meme</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1188216694" "The warehouse is bustling - Nemesis is quickly trying to get everything out of here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P668187198" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Nemesis Meme</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You get far away enough and activate the charges you placed, engulfing the Automaton Factory in flames. You watch the fires burn down all of the various plots and ploys that Nemesis had, making the world that much safer from him."

